    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I haven’t seen Kirsten in years - and it’s a lovely catchup. Once again it’s a lifelong relationship that seems to all come back the moment you see them again. We eat some pretty great eggy breakfasts that - obviously - are all served on English muffins. We all catchup on what we’ve been doing over the last while and laugh a lot.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "I haven’t seen Kirsten in years - and it’s a lovely catchup. Once again it’s a lifelong relationship that seems to all come back the moment you see them again. We eat some pretty great eggy breakfasts that - obviously - are all served on English muffins. We all catchup on what we’ve been doing over the last while and laugh a lot.",
