    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Kirsten heads off and Robynne, Jordan and I browse a second hand and book store. We hop onto the tube to which Robynne is amused how excited I am by the trains. We say our goodbyes and Jordan and I head back to Dave and Molly to collect their bags. They won’t be home for a little while so we do the classic thing of buying a beer from an off-licence shop and playing a game of backgammon in the park. ",
            "link": null
          },
