      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "And then I’m looking at a rather strange looking cat on the other side of the road. Or is it a dog? And then I realise that it’s a fox! Our walk is a success, we look at the Emerites stadium down the road and on the way back see three more foxes.",
